room_title: Escape room "The Night Out at the BAD GIRL, Аничка" by Code To Escape in Daytona Beach
room_address: 119 S Palmetto Ave Daytona Beach, FL 32114
room_description: You had an outstanding night out with your friends. Nobody knows the details but it looks that you are trapped in the room of Anichka. Russian girls are pretty, smart, they treat you special. It was a great place to spend all your hard-earned cash. Anichka looks okay, but not the kind of woman you’d want to mess with. You only have 60 minutes to leave her room or deal with her anger, by the way, you had no money to pay for the services last night…
